The paper deals with physical layer security in MIMO wiretap channels, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The proposed scheme involves antenna selection, which falls under networked systems (cs.NI) and multiple antennas (cs.MM). The paper also presents closed-form expressions for probability calculations, which is related to statistical mechanics (cs.SI).
